%section#benefits
  .container
    %h2
      What makes it great?
    .row.columns
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'users'
          %br
          Find new clients you love
        %p
          Join Uplink to find new challenging projects and get in touch with companies from Berlin, the rest of Germany, Switzerland, the UK, and the US. Whether you’re looking for the intimate, dynamic feel of a startup or the hustle and bustle of an agency or large company, you can find it through Uplink. Let us handle the job sourcing, so you can focus on what you do best - writing great code!
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'repeat'
          %br
          Skip clueless recruiters
        %p
          We are freelance developers ourselves, so we know that dealing with non-technical recruiters can be frustrating. Since Uplink is first and foremost a service for you - the freelancers - we understand your priorities and make them ours. This means we can honestly tell you about trickier customers or a project’s potential pitfalls. We are on your side and treat your time and attention with respect.
    .row.columns
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'envelope'
          %br
          No public profile, no listings
        %p
          You don’t need another public profile that must be kept up-to-date, or a list of irrelevant job descriptions you have to scroll through. With a little work done by us personally, not by an algorithm, we can save all our members a lot of time and frustration. We keep it simple, pre-select the jobs for you, and present them to you in a personal, non-automated email.
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'heart'
          %br
          Focus on Berlin
        %p
          In order to build a tight-knit network of like-minded developers, we currently focus on freelancers from Berlin. This lets us offer on-site developers to the startups and media companies of Berlin and grow organically through personal recommendations of our members. Soon we will roll out our service in Hamburg, Munich, Frankfurt and more cities across Germany and internationally. Stay tuned!
    .row.columns
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'clock-o'
          %br
          Timing is everything
        %p
          Are you busy in a project right now but already want to line up the next one? We know what a hassle it is to try to find a new project exactly when you need it. No worries, just tell us when you are available again and we can negotiate with interested companies on your behalf and let them know they might want to postpone (or advance) their projects to have you on their team.
      .col-sm-6
        %h3
          = icon 'euro'
          %br
          We know what you’re worth
        %p
          Negotiating a rate with a potential client can be the most stressful part of the whole project. This is why we make sure our clients know that 50€ is the minimum hourly rate of any freelancer in the Uplink network, and of course we will honour your personal hourly rate as well. Let us make sure you and the client are playing in the same ballpark before you even talk to them.

